WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:02.880
Several months later

00:03.400 --> 00:05.880
Under the strong pressure of Shilang's army

00:06.280 --> 00:10.120
Xuan Kingdom had to abandon Beiyu Pass and other lands north of the river

00:10.320 --> 00:12.160
And retreated to defend Tianhe

00:13.440 --> 00:16.440
Shilang fought at Tianhe for half a year

00:16.600 --> 00:18.840
But could never advance a single step

00:19.000 --> 00:21.600
Finally had to retreat north

00:22.320 --> 00:25.680
Xuan Kingdom also suffered heavy losses in this battle

00:26.480 --> 00:27.840
The loss of Beiyu Pass

00:28.000 --> 00:31.000
Signaled that Xuan Kingdom had no hope of northern expeditions

00:36.880 --> 00:38.600
The 36th year of Longwu

00:39.440 --> 00:42.280
Sikong Yao, who had sighed looking north for decades

00:42.560 --> 00:45.320
Finally died of illness in the capital, full of regret

00:45.720 --> 00:47.720
At the age of 57

00:48.200 --> 00:49.680
Later generations called him
